mapper.select:
WITH master AS ( SELECT , 徴収方法Newest.*, "UeT0511NenkinTokuchoKaifuJoho".* FROM "DbT2002FukaJohoTemp" AS "DbT2002FukaJohoTemp" LEFT JOIN () AS 徴収方法Newest ON "DbT2002FukaJohoTemp"."fukaNendo" = 徴収方法Newest."dbV2001ChoshuHoho_fukaNendo" AND "DbT2002FukaJohoTemp"."hihokenshaNo" = 徴収方法Newest."dbV2001ChoshuHoho_hihokenshaNo" AND 徴収方法Newest."dbV2001ChoshuHoho_kariNenkinNo" IS NOT NULL AND 徴収方法Newest."dbV2001ChoshuHoho_kariNenkinNo" <> '' LEFT JOIN rgdb."UeT0511NenkinTokuchoKaifuJoho" AS "UeT0511NenkinTokuchoKaifuJoho" ON "UeT0511NenkinTokuchoKaifuJoho"."gyomuCode" = 'DB' AND "UeT0511NenkinTokuchoKaifuJoho"."shoriNendo" = 徴収方法Newest."dbV2001ChoshuHoho_fukaNendo" AND "UeT0511NenkinTokuchoKaifuJoho"."tsuchiNaiyoCode" = '30' AND "UeT0511NenkinTokuchoKaifuJoho"."shoriTaishoYM" = 徴収方法Newest."dbV2001ChoshuHoho_fukaNendo"||'04' AND "UeT0511NenkinTokuchoKaifuJoho"."kisoNenkinNo" = 徴収方法Newest."dbV2001ChoshuHoho_kariNenkinNo" AND "UeT0511NenkinTokuchoKaifuJoho"."nenkinCode" = 徴収方法Newest."dbV2001ChoshuHoho_kariNenkinCode" ) SELECT master.*,
FROM master LEFT JOIN
( SELECT ARRAY_AGG(CAST (master."dbT2002Fuka_shikibetsuCode" AS TEXT)) FROM master ) AS "ShikibetsuTaisho" ON master."dbT2002Fuka_shikibetsuCode" = "ShikibetsuTaisho"."shikibetsuCode"
${出力順}
